{"tid":816762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得大灣區同當年南越國幾似","createTime":"2018-09-13T02:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T14:39:01.000Z","uid":209547,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d8a1647cd19ce3b3dc8ebe03194ef33f3069b193","tid":816762,"uid":209547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:58:22.000Z","msg":"介紹返, 南越國又稱南粵，在越南又稱為趙朝<br />\n是中國南部以至東南亞是最強和最富的王國<br />\n西漢出兵10萬發動對南越國的戰爭，並滅亡南越國，收南越人為己民，於是廣東的百越民族被北面的胡漢族漢化；成為漢奴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/105220_7dd41bf68e8145ef4cba2b3fdfe42275.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F105220_7dd41bf68e8145ef4cba2b3fdfe42275.jpg&h=f62a5963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/105221_54d0d51c2ce8d2b3d54971dee2c4fcb7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F105221_54d0d51c2ce8d2b3d54971dee2c4fcb7.png&h=0225c3cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d84fceb01602b047725b67543c9be47befc7932","tid":816762,"uid":209547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T13:01:28.000Z","msg":"冇人討論既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627830ea6cdb195ffaa0b1911356e28e33514464","tid":816762,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T13:03:43.000Z","msg":"廣東人祖先有機會係越南人？"},{"pid":"4c261dc31315a5f7756342641cb780045a9e05f0","tid":816762,"uid":181641,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"627830ea6cdb195ffaa0b1911356e28e33514464","tid":816762,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T13:03:43.000Z","msg":"廣東人祖先有機會係越南人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"南越<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9454f570c4507f2bb7fdc8fd8cf49863e099f273","tid":816762,"uid":132859,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T13:31:10.000Z","msg":"原來中共內部已經有南越復國主義嘅同志潛伏在内<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d038851b6d9822599402e99edb88f69c61b0cc37","tid":816762,"uid":209547,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9454f570c4507f2bb7fdc8fd8cf49863e099f273","tid":816762,"uid":132859,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T13:31:10.000Z","msg":"原來中共內部已經有南越復國主義嘅同志潛伏在内<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:53:39.000Z","msg":"秦末亂世時, 南越國係由秦國分裂獨立出黎, 然後慢慢富強起黎.<br />\n今次中共設大灣區, 隨時係一個炸彈,<br />\n只要區內經濟發展到一定水平, 土地又有返咁上下, 要再次分裂獨立並非難事.<br />\n到時粵語就成為大灣國官語, 香港為首都"},{"pid":"4ccee7e3e8e1780d54e712734a038bd981425bc8","tid":816762,"uid":209547,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"627830ea6cdb195ffaa0b1911356e28e33514464","tid":816762,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T13:03:43.000Z","msg":"廣東人祖先有機會係越南人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:56:38.000Z","msg":"當時好多漢族黎左嶺南之地, 同百越人交集.<br />\n情況就好似中共建國後好多人移民廣東同香港.<br />\n<br />\n研究顯示，大部份廣東人的Y-染色體（父親的祖先）是漢族，而大部份廣東人的mtDNA（母系祖先）是百越族<br />\n<br />\n廣東人父系：越人O1血統20%，秦漢漢族血統20%，唐朝漢族(此時漢族因為北魏漢化政策加入了大量北魏鮮卑人血統)血統30%，宋朝漢族血統30% <br />\n廣東人母系：越人血統80%，漢族血統20%"},{"pid":"4ae54aa73ea9cfe845bb86038ae1423340efacd7","tid":816762,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:17:32.000Z","msg":"最最最重要係拉埋香港，有香港個名就嘜都掂晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b22c00ec23230e1a7c4472ca788d3b91ae861f","tid":816762,"uid":209547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"有冇歷史/政治撚討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caba51febe96402d94d7202b33d3753b5e03b49c","tid":816762,"uid":209547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T11:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/0